                "type": "text",
                "text": " -- This is a tough one, as adventure games can be so different from one another. I'm going to answer with more than one because they are the \"best\" in their respective categories. Classic adventure game: Day of the tentacle, though I'm very much enjoying Thimbleweed Park now. Choice-based dramatic adventure game: Telltale's The Wolf Among Us. And best adventure game that defies categorization is Kentucky Route Zero."
              }
